item.description:
The Stack vDB REST API mirrors the Qdrant REST API as far as possible. To that end, `Libraries` in Stack vDB are analogous to `Collections` in Qdrant. The `Library` resource exposes the following endpoints:

1. List all Libraries
    
2. Create
    
3. Check if exists by ID
    
4. Get by ID
    
5. Delete by ID
    
6. Get all Chunks
